<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - Stretch</title>
  <%- include ../../partials/_head %>
  <link rel='stylesheet' href='styles/stretch.min.css'>
</head>
<body class="stretch stretch-portal">
  <%- include ../../partials/_menu %>
  <%- include ../../partials/_stretch-subnav %>
  <main class="wrapper case-study">
    <header class="case-header">
      <div class="case-header-content bottom container">
        <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Stretch Portal</h5>
        <h1 class="case-header-tagline">The&nbsp;best&nbsp;seat&nbsp;in&#32;<br />the&nbsp;house</h1>
        <h6 class="case-header-type">Live Viewer Portal</h6>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-exec-summary padded blue">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="case-exec-summary-text">We listened to viewers and gave them what they want: an intuitive, interactive live event viewer, from smartphone to smart TV.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-breakdown padded light-black">
      <div class="container row between">
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            A Crowded Live&nbsp;<br />Event Space
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            Most portals are chaotic, unrelated clips and misleading thumbnails. How can a modern viewer feel at home&nbsp;online?
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Re-centering on&nbsp;<br />Experience
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            Content now gets organized in a familiar way. And live events invite participation, so no viewer feels left&nbsp;out.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
          <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Research</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Interaction Design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block bg-image extra-padded white" data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/mobile-first-bg.svg" style="background-position: top">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block column half-md two-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="frame frame-mobile-horizontal shadow lighter sr-left">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/mobile-first.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column order-top-xs gutter-bottom-mobile half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
            <h4 class="case-block-heading">Mobile-first</h4>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              The data couldn't be clearer: mobile is where the future of streaming video is headed. For those craving a bigger experience, our fully-flexible UI delivers up to giant, HD&nbsp;screens.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="1440" data-height="800">
        <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/rugby.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block row padded gray stretch-wave stretch-portal-tangible">
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column half-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content container gutter-right padded-bottom">
          <h4 class="case-block-heading">Make it tangible</h4>
          <p class="case-block-text">
              We found that users intuitively had an idea of what an 'event' was, so we turned this mental concept into an intuitive way to get&nbsp;around.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block column column-block gutter-left-mobile half-md">
        <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="735" data-height="650">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/tangible1.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-reveal">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/tangible2.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-stagger-right">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/tangible3.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-stagger-right">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/tangible4.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-stagger-right">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/tangible5.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-stagger-right">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top blue stretch-portal-personal">
      <div class="row container">
      <div class="inner-block column column-block half-md">
          <div class="frame frame-mobile shadow lighter sr-bottom">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/portal.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column order-top-xs half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left padded-bottom">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">A personal touch</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
                No one wants to miss out when something's live. Our personal account system empowers each user to subscribe to what they love, and get timely reminders on what's&nbsp;next.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded black">
      <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Be immersive</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Users can react to live events in real time. They can also browse through in-depth stats, and even make donations - whatever each event calls for.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block gray-langur-adventure">
        <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="2880" data-height="1626">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/immersive-bg.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/reaction1.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-reveal">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/reaction2.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-reveal">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/reaction3.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-reveal">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/reaction4.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-reveal">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/reaction5.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-reveal">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/emoji1.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/emoji2.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/emoji3.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/emoji4.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/emoji5.png" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-stagger-top">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded dark-blue stretch-portal-community">
      <div class="container row">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile column half-md">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-right">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">For&nbsp;communities that&nbsp;scale</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
                From sprawling athletic conferences to community events, all of the content is intuitive, dynamic, and easy&nbsp;to&nbsp;find.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column column-block half-md">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="732" data-height="625">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/community-container.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/community1.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image shadow absolute-top sr-stagger-right">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/portal/community2.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image shadow absolute-bottom sr-stagger-right">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-referral row">
      <div class="inner-block padded column absolute-center-xs half-md gray">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="case-referral-blockquote">Long quote here from Jordan Duvall or another Stretch team member</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block padded column half-md blue">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
          <p class="case-referral-text">Long quote here from Jordan Duvall or another Stretch team member lorem ipsum dolot sit amet. Long quote here from Jordan Duvall or another Stretch team member lorem ipsum dolot sit amet.</p>
          <p class="case-referral-author">Jordan Duvall, <em>Position, Stretch Live</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block bg-image padded-top purple" data-normal="./images/work/stretch/business-bg.jpg">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block column column-block align-self-bottom half-md two-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop edge-bottom lighter shadow sr-bottom lazy-ratio" data-width="954" data-height="932">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/stretch/business.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column order-top-xs half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left padded-bottom">
            <h4 class="case-block-tagline">Next</h4>
            <h2 class="case-block-heading lg">The CMS</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text lg">
              The internet's most intuitive, powerful way to put on&nbsp;a&nbsp;show
            </p>
            <a href="./work/stretch/cms" class="btn btn-box alt">View Case Study</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-block padded">
      <a href="./work/upfront" class="cta-button cta-button-left" title="Previous Case">Previous Case</a>
      <div class="cta-content container">
        <div class="cta-text">Sometimes, you find something that just works.</div>
        <a href="/approach" class="btn btn-text icon-arrow">See Our Approach</a>
      </div>
      <a href="./work/ijr" class="cta-button cta-button-right" title="Next Case">Next Case</a>
    </section>

    <%- include ../../partials/_footer %>
  </main>

  <%- include ../../partials/_footer-scripts %>

</body>
</html>
